  "text": "V is a permeate volume, A is the membrane surface area, t is filtration time, and P is operational pressure. BSA concentration in permeate and retentate was then analyzed using a spectrophotometer. Rejection capability of the membrane can be determined using the equations as follows [CITATION_1] :",
